tivate appropriate emotion regulation strategies.<br><br><\\/p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/digiuth.com\\/uploads\\/digiuth.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" tt-mode=\\\"file\\\" tt-link-url=\\\"\\\" tt-link-target=\\\"\\\" tt-link-mode=\\\"url\\\" class=\\\"\\\"><p>Experiments were conducted on seven young people with symptoms of depression. I don\'t want to bother you with unnecessary details so I will cut to two main sections of the experiments. (you can read the whole experiment <a target=\\\"_blank\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.frontiersin.org\\/articles\\/10.3389\\/fpsyg.2019.01199\\/full\\\" tt-mode=\\\"url\\\">here<\\/a>)<br><br><\\/p><img src=\\\"https:\\/\\/digiuth.com\\/uploads\\/digiuth.png\\\" alt=\\\"\\\" title=\\\"\\\" tt-mode=\\\"file\\\" tt-link-url=\\\"\\\" tt-link-target=\\\"\\\" tt-link-mode=\\\"url\\\" class=\\\"\\\"><p><br><br><\\/p>\"}'),
