aduate of ADA University\'s Faculty of Computer Engineering. In 2019, she won the Erasmus + program and continued her education at Istanbul City University for 1 semester in January-May. In 2018, she won the Global Startup Lab program held by MIT University in Azerbaijan and participated in 6-week startup trainings organized by MIT. Fidan has many certifications, including \\u2018Oracle Certified Associated\\u2019. During her university years, she has participated in many internship programs, including Azersun Holding, TelecomInvest companies. Since September 2020, she has been working at Azerconnect LLC as a specialist in IT Corporate Platforms.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\"},\"linkedin_link\":null,\"facebook_link\":null,\"instagram_link\":null,\"updated_at\":\"2022-04-06T08:42:25.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-04-06T08:42:25.000000Z\",\"id\":6}'),
