(341, '95ff3d1b-0d21-42e6-ade1-f59364eba45c', 33, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 10, 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 10, 'App\\Models\\Trainer', 10, '', 'finished', '', '2022-04-06 08:45:43', '2022-04-06 08:45:43', NULL, '{\"image\":\"LYeLv4kamEQrrriOlXCKFxBbgXcxU4cgFIRPSZ3V.jpg\",\"fullname\":{\"en\":\"\\u0130lham Ahmadov\",\"az\":\"\\u0130lham \\u018fhm\\u0259dov\"},\"position\":{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"},\"content\":{\"az\":\"<div>\\u0130lham \\u018fhm\\u0259dov bakalavr t\\u0259hsilini Amerikan\\u0131n Hartwick Kollecind\\u0259 \\u0259ld\\u0259 etmi\\u015fdir. Bu layih\\u0259 \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 kommunikasiyan\\u0131n \\u0259saslar\\u0131 v\\u0259 idar\\u0259 edilm\\u0259si m\\u00f6vzusunda kurs haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Hal-haz\\u0131rda milli televiziyalar\\u0131n birind\\u0259 ba\\u015f redaktor v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131r. O, eyni zamanda pe\\u015f\\u0259kar t\\u0259rc\\u00fcm\\u0259\\u00e7idir v\\u0259 m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif m\\u00f6vzu v\\u0259 janrlarda ingilis-az\\u0259rbaycan-rus dill\\u0259rind\\u0259 yaz\\u0131l\\u0131 v\\u0259 \\u015fifahi t\\u0259rc\\u00fcm\\u0259l\\u0259r edir. O, \\u00fcmid edir ki, kursdan faydalananlar \\u00e7ox olacaq v\\u0259 burda \\u0259ld\\u0259 etdikl\\u0259ri bilikl\\u0259ri h\\u0259m pe\\u015f\\u0259kar h\\u0259yatlar\\u0131nda, h\\u0259m d\\u0259 \\u015f\\u0259xsi h\\u0259yatlar\\u0131nda t\\u0259tbiq ed\\u0259c\\u0259kl\\u0259r.<\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Ilham Ahmadov received his bachelor\'s degree from Hartwick College in the United States. Within the framework of this project, he developed a course on the basics and management of communication. He is currently the editor-in-chief of one of the national televisions. He is also a professional translator and provides written and oral translations in English-Azerbaijani-Russian on various topics and genres. He hopes that there will be many beneficiaries of the course and will apply the