(724, '965d8be2-bc0f-4c91-b69f-95b4bac68b98', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Course', 63, 'App\\Models\\Course', 63, 'App\\Models\\Course', 63, '', 'finished', '', '2022-05-23 05:53:50', '2022-05-23 05:53:50', NULL, '{\"user_id\":63,\"course_category_id\":9,\"title\":{\"en\":\"Sosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n \\u0259saslar\\u0131\",\"az\":\"Sosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n \\u0259saslar\\u0131\"},\"about\":{\"en\":\"How can we create innovative and effective solutions to social problems in our society and in the world? In this course, we will try to find an answer to this question through social entrepreneurship. In the course you will get acquainted with the concept of social entrepreneurship and use it to learn the basics of how to solve existing social problems in society. Social entrepreneurship describes the identification and sustainable use of opportunities for social change. We will introduce you to real social entrepreneurship examples and learn how to identify a problem to solve social or environmental problems, understand contextual realities, develop solutions and plan effective implementation, and show you the steps to take in the process of creating a social business.\",\"az\":\"C\\u0259miyy\\u0259timizd\\u0259 v\\u0259  d\\u00fcnyada sosial probleml\\u0259r\\u0259 yenilik\\u00e7i v\\u0259 effektiv h\\u0259ll yollar\\u0131n\\u0131 nec\\u0259 yarada bil\\u0259rik? Bu kursda biz bu suala sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q \\u00fcz\\u0259rind\\u0259n cavab tapma\\u011fa  \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015faca\\u011f\\u0131q. Kursda siz sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q anlay\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f ola v\\u0259 bundan istifad\\u0259 ed\\u0259r\\u0259k c\\u0259miyy\\u0259td\\u0259 m\\u00f6vcud olan sosial probleml\\u0259ri nec\\u0259 h\\u0259ll etm\\u0259k bar\\u0259d\\u0259 ilkin m\\u0259lumatlar  \\u00f6yr\\u0259n\\u0259c\\u0259ksiniz. Sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q sosial d\\u0259yi\\u015fiklik yaratmaq imkanlar\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u015fkar edilm\\u0259sini v\\u0259 davaml\\u0131 istifad\\u0259sini t\\u0259svir edir. Biz sizi real sosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n n\\u00fcmun\\u0259l\\u0259ri il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f ed\\u0259c\\u0259yik v\\u0259 sosial v\\u0259 ya \\u0259traf m\\u00fchit probleml\\u0259rini h\\u0259ll etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn  problemi nec\\u0259 m\\u00fc\\u0259yy\\u0259nl\\u0259\\u015fdirm\\u0259yi, kontekstual reall\\u0131qlar\\u0131 ba\\u015fa d\\u00fc\\u015fm\\u0259yi, h\\u0259ll yolu haz\\u0131rlama\\u011f\\u0131 v\\u0259 effektiv t\\u0259tbiqini planla\\u015fd\\u0131rma\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00f6yr\\u0259n\\u0259c\\u0259k v\\u0259 sosial biznesin  yarad\\u0131lmas\\u0131 prosesind\\u0259 at\\u0131lmal\\u0131 add\\u0131mlar\\u0131 g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259c\\u0259yik.\"},\"language\":\"Az\\u0259rbaycan\",\"course_duration\":\"60\",\"section_count\":\"2\",\"lecture_count\":\"15\",\"image\":\"u5xgS6ey67cJcLxJtunyEPdozIidse4aBi3e8bBH.png\",\"tags\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Social\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Sosial\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Sahibkarl\\u0131q\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"sosialbiznes\\\"}]\",\"content\":{\"en\":\"<div>How can we create innovative and effective solutions to social problems in our society and in the world? In this course, we will try to find an answer to this question through social entrepreneurship. In the course you will get acquainted with the concept of social entrepreneurship and use it to learn the basics of how to solve existing social problems in society. Social entrepreneurship describes the identification and sustainable use of opportunities for social change. We will introduce you to real social entrepreneurship examples and learn how to identify a problem to solve social or environmental problems, understand contextual realities, develop solutions and plan effective implementation, and show you the steps to take in the process of creating a social business.<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>C\\u0259miyy\\u0259timizd\\u0259 v\\u0259&nbsp; d\\u00fcnyada sosial probleml\\u0259r\\u0259 yenilik\\u00e7i v\\u0259 effektiv h\\u0259ll yollar\\u0131n\\u0131 nec\\u0259 yarada bil\\u0259rik? Bu kursda biz bu suala sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q \\u00fcz\\u0259rind\\u0259n cavab tapma\\u011fa&nbsp; \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015faca\\u011f\\u0131q. Kursda siz sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q anlay\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f ola v\\u0259 bundan istifad\\u0259 ed\\u0259r\\u0259k c\\u0259miyy\\u0259td\\u0259 m\\u00f6vcud olan sosial probleml\\u0259ri nec\\u0259 h\\u0259ll etm\\u0259k bar\\u0259d\\u0259 ilkin m\\u0259lumatlar&nbsp; \\u00f6yr\\u0259n\\u0259c\\u0259ksiniz. Sosial sahibkarl\\u0131q sosial d\\u0259yi\\u015fiklik yaratmaq imkanlar\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u015fkar edilm\\u0259sini v\\u0259 davaml\\u0131 istifad\\u0259sini t\\u0259svir edir. Biz sizi real sosial sahibkarl\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n n\\u00fcmun\\u0259l\\u0259ri il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f ed\\u0259c\\u0259yik v\\u0259 sosial v\\u0259 ya \\u0259traf m\\u00fchit probleml\\u0259rini h\\u0259ll etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn&nbsp; problemi nec\\u0259 m\\u00fc\\u0259yy\\u0259nl\\u0259\\u015fdirm\\u0259yi, kontekstual reall\\u0131qlar\\u0131 ba\\u015fa d\\u00fc\\u015fm\\u0259yi, h\\u0259ll yolu haz\\u0131rlama\\u011f\\u0131 v\\u0259 effektiv t\\u0259tbiqini planla\\u015fd\\u0131rma\\u011f\\u0131 \\u00f6yr\\u0259n\\u0259c\\u0259k v\\u0259 sosial biznesin&nbsp; yarad\\u0131lmas\\u0131 prosesind\\u0259 at\\u0131lmal\\u0131 add\\u0131mlar\\u0131 g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259c\\u0259yik.<\\/div>\"},\"updated_at\":\"2022-05-23T05:53:50.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-05-23T05:53:50.000000Z\",\"id\":63,\"rating\":\"0.00\"}'),
