ondunun \\\\u201cVi\\\\u015feqrad Qrantlar\\\\u0131\\\\u201d vasit\\\\u0259sil\\\\u0259 maliyy\\\\u0259l\\\\u0259\\\\u015fdirilir. Fondun \\\\u0259sas missiyas\\\\u0131 M\\\\u0259rk\\\\u0259zi Avropada davaml\\\\u0131 regional \\\\u0259m\\\\u0259kda\\\\u015fl\\\\u0131q \\\\u00fc\\\\u00e7\\\\u00fcn ideyalar\\\\u0131 t\\\\u0259\\\\u015fviq etm\\\\u0259kd\\\\u0259n ibar\\\\u0259tdir.<\\\\\\/div>\\\"}\"}'),
(858, '966d2f50-0373-4184-bee4-e8b8a0414e1f', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Course', 64, 'App\\Models\\Course', 64, 'App\\Models\\Course', 64, '', 'finished', '', '2022-05-31 00:28:13', '2022-05-31 00:28:13', NULL, '{\"user_id\":11,\"course_category_id\":12,\"title\":{\"en\":\"How to build a successful career?\",\"az\":\"U\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 nec\\u0259 qurmal\\u0131?\"},\"about\":{\"en\":\"Welcome to the \\\"How to build a successful career?\\\" training program. Where do you see yourself in the future? Are you satisfied with your current career? This training program is designed for anyone who is just starting their career or wants to make a change. The goal is to be able to design a career path in line with personal values, interests, personality and skills, to anticipate possible obstacles, and to build strategies and plans in line with career goals. The strategy of the training program is as follows:\\r\\n1. Training is application based.\\r\\n2. Building a successful career requires not only knowledge and techniques, but also psychological training. This training will introduce you to development theories while creating your own awareness.\\r\\n3. All information within the training is scientifically based.\\r\\n4. The program is divided into special topics and allows the audience to participate in the training from the stage they need.\\r\\n\\r\\nIn a successful career building training, you will first be introduced to a variety of tools to identify your characteristics - personality type, values, skills and career interests. At the next stage, you will get acquainted with the trends and areas of activity in the labor market. Then, based on the information obtained, personal career goals will be selected through specific strategies.\\r\\nThis training program requires technical skills such as working with search engines and using social media.\",\"az\":\"\\\"U\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 nec\\u0259 qurmal\\u0131?\\\" t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131na xo\\u015f g\\u0259lmisiniz. G\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcz\\u00fc harda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcrs\\u00fcn\\u00fcz? Hal-haz\\u0131rki karyeran\\u0131zdan m\\u0259mnunsunuz? Bu t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131 karyeras\\u0131na yeni ba\\u015flayan v\\u0259 ya d\\u0259yi\\u015fiklik etm\\u0259k ist\\u0259y\\u0259n h\\u0259r k\\u0259s \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn n\\u0259z\\u0259rd\\u0259 tutulmu\\u015fdur. M\\u0259qs\\u0259d \\u015f\\u0259xsi d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259r\\u0259, maraqlara, \\u015f\\u0259xsiyy\\u0259t\\u0259 v\\u0259 bacar\\u0131qlara uy\\u011fun karyera yolunu dizayn ed\\u0259 bilm\\u0259k, m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn olan \\u0259ng\\u0259ll\\u0259ri \\u00f6nc\\u0259d\\u0259n g\\u00f6r\\u0259 bilm\\u0259k v\\u0259 karyera m\\u0259qs\\u0259dl\\u0259rin\\u0259 uy\\u011fun strategiya v\\u0259 plam qurmaqd\\u0131r. T\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131n\\u0131n strategiyas\\u0131 a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131dak\\u0131lardan ibar\\u0259tdir:\\r\\n1. T\\u0259tbiq \\u0259sasl\\u0131d\\u0131r. Bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n inki\\u015faf etdirilm\\u0259si m\\u0259qs\\u0259di il\\u0259 t\\u0259lim t\\u0259tbiqi tap\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131qlar\\u0131 t\\u0259m\\u0259l alaraq davam edir.\\r\\n2. U\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131n qurulmas\\u0131 bilik v\\u0259 texnikalardan \\u0259lav\\u0259, psixoloji haz\\u0131rl\\u0131q t\\u0259l\\u0259b edir. Bu t\\u0259lim \\u00f6z f\\u0259rqind\\u0259lik yaratmaqla b\\u0259rab\\u0259r inki\\u015faf n\\u0259z\\u0259riyy\\u0259l\\u0259ri il\\u0259 sizi tan\\u0131\\u015f ed\\u0259c\\u0259k.\\r\\n3. T\\u0259lim daxilind\\u0259ki b\\u00fct\\u00fcn m\\u0259lumatlar elmi \\u0259sasl\\u0131d\\u0131r.\\r\\n4. Proqram x\\u00fcsusi m\\u00f6vzular \\u015f\\u0259klind\\u0259 ayr\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r v\\u0259 izl\\u0259yiciy\\u0259 ehtiyac\\u0131 olan m\\u0259rh\\u0259l\\u0259d\\u0259n t\\u0259lim\\u0259 qat\\u0131lma\\u011fa imkan yarad\\u0131r.\\r\\n\\r\\nU\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 qurulmas\\u0131 t\\u0259limind\\u0259 siz\\u0259 ilk \\u00f6nc\\u0259 \\u00f6z x\\u00fcsusiyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rinizi - \\u015f\\u0259xsiyy\\u0259t tipini, d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259ri, bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131 v\\u0259 karyera maraqlar\\u0131n\\u0131 m\\u00fc\\u0259yy\\u0259nl\\u0259\\u015fdirm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif al\\u0259tl\\u0259r t\\u0259qdim olunacaqd\\u0131r. N\\u00f6vb\\u0259ti m\\u0259rh\\u0259l\\u0259d\\u0259 i\\u015f bazar\\u0131nda olan trendl\\u0259rl\\u0259, f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t sah\\u0259l\\u0259ri il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f olacaqs\\u0131n\\u0131z. Daha sonra \\u0259ld\\u0259 olunan m\\u0259lumatlar\\u0131 t\\u0259m\\u0259l alaraq, x\\u00fcsusi strategiyalar vasit\\u0259si il\\u0259 \\u015f\\u0259xsi karyera m\\u0259qs\\u0259dl\\u0259r se\\u00e7il\\u0259c\\u0259kdir. \\r\\nBu t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131 axtar\\u0131\\u015f sisteml\\u0259ri il\\u0259 i\\u015fl\\u0259m\\u0259k v\\u0259 sosial \\u015f\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259 istifad\\u0259si kimi texniki bacar\\u0131qlar t\\u0259l\\u0259b edir.\"},\"language\":\"Azerbaijani\",\"course_duration\":\"120\",\"section_count\":\"6\",\"lecture_count\":\"21\",\"image\":\"H9rFTKlYkpYYtYuZ0FQsP67PgBwCSaQgqT134FyL.png\",\"tags\":\"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Human\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"resources\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"career\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"development\\\"}]\",\"content\":{\"en\":\"<div>Welcome to the \\\"How to build a successful career?\\\" training program. Where do you see yourself in the future? Are you satisfied with your current career? This training program is designed for anyone who is just starting their career or wants to make a change. The goal is to be able to design a career path in line with personal values, interests, personality and skills, to anticipate possible obstacles, and to build strategies and plans in line with career goals. The strategy of the training program is as follows:<br>1. Training is application based.<br>2. Building a successful career requires not only knowledge and techniques, but also psychological training. This training will introduce you to development theories while creating your own awareness.<br>3. All information within the training is scientifically based.<br>4. The program is divided into special topics and allows the audience to participate in the training from the stage they need.<br><br>In a successful career building training, you will first be introduced to a variety of tools to identify your characteristics - personality type, values, skills and career interests. At the next stage, you will get acquainted with the trends and areas of activity in the labor market. Then, based on the information obtained, personal career goals will be selected through specific strategies.<br>This training program requires technical skills such as working with search engines and using social media.<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div><br>\\\"U\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 nec\\u0259 qurmal\\u0131?\\\" t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131na xo\\u015f g\\u0259lmisiniz. G\\u0259l\\u0259c\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\u00f6z\\u00fcn\\u00fcz\\u00fc harda g\\u00f6r\\u00fcrs\\u00fcn\\u00fcz? Hal-haz\\u0131rki karyeran\\u0131zdan m\\u0259mnunsunuz? Bu t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131 karyeras\\u0131na yeni ba\\u015flayan v\\u0259 ya d\\u0259yi\\u015fiklik etm\\u0259k ist\\u0259y\\u0259n h\\u0259r k\\u0259s \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn n\\u0259z\\u0259rd\\u0259 tutulmu\\u015fdur. M\\u0259qs\\u0259d \\u015f\\u0259xsi d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259r\\u0259, maraqlara, \\u015f\\u0259xsiyy\\u0259t\\u0259 v\\u0259 bacar\\u0131qlara uy\\u011fun karyera yolunu dizayn ed\\u0259 bilm\\u0259k, m\\u00fcmk\\u00fcn olan \\u0259ng\\u0259ll\\u0259ri \\u00f6nc\\u0259d\\u0259n g\\u00f6r\\u0259 bilm\\u0259k v\\u0259 karyera m\\u0259qs\\u0259dl\\u0259rin\\u0259 uy\\u011fun strategiya v\\u0259 plam qurmaqd\\u0131r. T\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131n\\u0131n strategiyas\\u0131 a\\u015fa\\u011f\\u0131dak\\u0131lardan ibar\\u0259tdir:<br>1. T\\u0259tbiq \\u0259sasl\\u0131d\\u0131r. Bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n inki\\u015faf etdirilm\\u0259si m\\u0259qs\\u0259di il\\u0259 t\\u0259lim t\\u0259tbiqi tap\\u015f\\u0131r\\u0131qlar\\u0131 t\\u0259m\\u0259l alaraq davam edir.<br>2. U\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131n qurulmas\\u0131 bilik v\\u0259 texnikalardan \\u0259lav\\u0259, psixoloji haz\\u0131rl\\u0131q t\\u0259l\\u0259b edir. Bu t\\u0259lim \\u00f6z f\\u0259rqind\\u0259lik yaratmaqla b\\u0259rab\\u0259r inki\\u015faf n\\u0259z\\u0259riyy\\u0259l\\u0259ri il\\u0259 sizi tan\\u0131\\u015f ed\\u0259c\\u0259k.<br>3. T\\u0259lim daxilind\\u0259ki b\\u00fct\\u00fcn m\\u0259lumatlar elmi \\u0259sasl\\u0131d\\u0131r.<br>4. Proqram x\\u00fcsusi m\\u00f6vzular \\u015f\\u0259klind\\u0259 ayr\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r v\\u0259 izl\\u0259yiciy\\u0259 ehtiyac\\u0131 olan m\\u0259rh\\u0259l\\u0259d\\u0259n t\\u0259lim\\u0259 qat\\u0131lma\\u011fa imkan yarad\\u0131r.<br><br>U\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 qurulmas\\u0131 t\\u0259limind\\u0259 siz\\u0259 ilk \\u00f6nc\\u0259 \\u00f6z x\\u00fcsusiyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rinizi - \\u015f\\u0259xsiyy\\u0259t tipini, d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259ri, bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131 v\\u0259 karyera maraqlar\\u0131n\\u0131 m\\u00fc\\u0259yy\\u0259nl\\u0259\\u015fdirm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif al\\u0259tl\\u0259r t\\u0259qdim olunacaqd\\u0131r. N\\u00f6vb\\u0259ti m\\u0259rh\\u0259l\\u0259d\\u0259 i\\u015f bazar\\u0131nda olan trendl\\u0259rl\\u0259, f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t sah\\u0259l\\u0259ri il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f olacaqs\\u0131n\\u0131z. Daha sonra \\u0259ld\\u0259 olunan m\\u0259lumatlar\\u0131 t\\u0259m\\u0259l alaraq, x\\u00fcsusi strategiyalar vasit\\u0259si il\\u0259 \\u015f\\u0259xsi karyera m\\u0259qs\\u0259dl\\u0259r se\\u00e7il\\u0259c\\u0259kdir.&nbsp;<br>Bu t\\u0259lim proqram\\u0131 axtar\\u0131\\u015f sisteml\\u0259ri il\\u0259 i\\u015fl\\u0259m\\u0259k v\\u0259 sosial \\u015f\\u0259b\\u0259k\\u0259 istifad\\u0259si kimi texniki bacar\\u0131qlar t\\u0259l\\u0259b edir.<\\/div>\"},\"updated_at\":\"2022-05-31T00:28:13.000000Z\",\"created_at\":\"2022-05-31T00:28:13.000000Z\",\"id\":64,\"rating\":\"