(959, '98a23e82-e11f-4a66-8cac-f8fee3f1b5d8', 52, 'Create', 'App\\Models\\Team', 15, 'App\\Models\\Team', 15, 'App\\Models\\Team', 15, '', 'finished', '', '2023-03-07 21:53:28', '2023-03-07 21:53:28', NULL, '{\"image\":\"mo8wFKLqMEje0UImO0w1efB0Snp1WKUbw71jGID4.jpg\",\"fullname\":{\"en\":\"Heydar Rzayev\",\"az\":\"Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev\"},\"position\":{\"en\":\"Project Manager\",\"az\":\"Layih\\u0259 meneceri\"},\"content\":{\"en\":\"<div>Heydar Rzayev graduated from ADA University with a degree in International Relations in 2020. Since 2019, he has worked as a board member and project manager at the Erasmus Student Network public union, which operates in the field of higher education. During his tenure, he won and implemented grants from various organizations such as ESAA, Visegrad and ESN International. Heydar Rzayev, who is currently pursuing a master\'s degree as an Erasmus Mundus scholar, worked as an intern at the UNESCO Institute for Lifelong Learning and the Agency for Quality Assurance in Education of the Republic of the Azerbaijan. He is currently working as a leading specialist in the Department of Strategic Research in Education of the Institute of Education of the Republic of Azerbaijan. When writing Digiuth project, Heydar\\u2019s main goal was to increase the access of Azerbaijani youth, especially young people living in our regions, to additional\\/ extracurricular education. He hopes that Digiuth will achieve his goal and play a major role in the personal development of young people of Azerbaijan.<br><br><\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev 2020-ci ild\\u0259 ADA Universitetinin Beyn\\u0259lxalq M\\u00fcnasib\\u0259tl\\u0259r fak\\u00fclt\\u0259sini bitirmi\\u015fdir. 2019-cu ild\\u0259n ali t\\u0259hsil sah\\u0259sind\\u0259 f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259n \\\"Erasmus T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259 T\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u0131\\\" ictimai birliyind\\u0259 idar\\u0259 hey\\u0259tinin \\u00fczv\\u00fc v\\u0259 layih\\u0259 meneceri v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. F\\u0259aliyy\\u0259td\\u0259 oldu\\u011fu m\\u00fcdd\\u0259td\\u0259 o, \\\"ESAA\\\", \\\"Visegrad\\\" v\\u0259 \\\"ESN International\\\" kimi m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlardan qrantlar qazanm\\u0131\\u015f v\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irmi\\u015fdir. Haz\\u0131rda magistratura pill\\u0259sind\\u0259 t\\u0259hsilini \\\"Erasmus Mundus\\\" t\\u0259qa\\u00fcd\\u00e7\\u00fcs\\u00fc olaraq davam etdir\\u0259n Heyd\\u0259r Rzayev t\\u0259hsil ald\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131 d\\u00f6vrd\\u0259 YUNESKO \\u00d6m\\u00fcr Boyu T\\u0259hshil \\u0130nstitutunda v\\u0259 Az\\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\\u0131n\\u0131n T\\u0259hsild\\u0259 Keyfiyy\\u0259t T\\u0259minat\\u0131 Agentliyind\\u0259&nbsp; t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259\\u00e7i olaraq \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Hal-haz\\u0131rda Az\\u0259rbaycan Respublikas\\u0131n\\u0131n T\\u0259hsil \\u0130nstitutunun T\\u0259hsild\\u0259 strateji t\\u0259dqiqatlar \\u015f\\u00f6b\\u0259sind\\u0259 apar\\u0131c\\u0131 m\\u00fct\\u0259x\\u0259ssis v\\u0259zif\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131r. Heyd\\u0259rin Digiuth proyektini yazark\\u0259n \\u0259sas m\\u0259qs\\u0259di Az\\u0259rbaycan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rinin x\\u00fcsusil\\u0259 d\\u0259 b\\u00f6lg\\u0259l\\u0259rimizd\\u0259 ya\\u015fayan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rin \\u0259lav\\u0259\\/m\\u0259kt\\u0259bd\\u0259nk\\u0259nar t\\u0259hsil\\u0259 \\u00e7\\u0131x\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131n\\u0131 art\\u0131rmaq idi. O, \\u00fcmid edir ki, Digiuth \\u00f6z m\\u0259qs\\u0259din\\u0259 \\u00e7atacaq v\\u0259 Az\\u0259rbaycan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259rinin \\u015f\\u0259xsi inki\\u015faf\\u0131nda b\\u00f6y\\u00fck rol oynayacaq.&nbsp;<br><br><\\/div>\"},\"linkedin_link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.linkedin.com\\/in\\/heydar-rzayev-21a08018a\\/\",\"facebook_link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/r.heydar85\",\"instagram_link\":\"https:\\/\\/www.instagram.com\\/heydar_r_\\/\",\"updated_at\":\"2023-