(59, '{\"en\":\"The video lesson discusses the concept and methods of non-formal education. Students are given general information about education, and then certain concepts are explained with examples. The main purpose of the course is to provide students with detailed information about the different methods of non-formal education.\",\"az\":\"Video d\\u0259rslikd\\u0259 qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsilin anlay\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 v\\u0259 metodlar\\u0131 haqq\\u0131nda dan\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131l\\u0131r. T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 t\\u0259hsil haqq\\u0131nda \\u00fcmumi m\\u0259lumat verilir, daha sonra is\\u0259 m\\u00fc\\u0259yy\\u0259n anlay\\u0131\\u015flar n\\u00fcmun\\u0259l\\u0259rl\\u0259 izah edilir. D\\u0259rsliyin \\u0259sas m\\u0259qs\\u0259di t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsilin m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif metodlar\\u0131n\\u0131 detall\\u0131 \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 \\u00e7atd\\u0131rmaqd\\u0131r.\"}', 'Azrbaycan', '60', 9, 4, 64, 11, '{\"en\":\"Non-formal Education\",\"az\":\"Qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsil n\\u0259dir?\"}', 'CuC2xFa0GFS0RCBAyl6gpzZCxaCrQ8xlOgmV6mj2.png', '{\"az\":\"<div>Video d\\u0259rslikd\\u0259 qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsilin anlay\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131 v\\u0259 metodlar\\u0131 haqq\\u0131nda dan\\u0131\\u015f\\u0131l\\u0131r. T\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 t\\u0259hsil haqq\\u0131nda \\u00fcmumi m\\u0259lumat verilir, daha sonra is\\u0259 m\\u00fc\\u0259yy\\u0259n anlay\\u0131\\u015flar n\\u00fcmun\\u0259l\\u0259rl\\u0259 izah edilir. D\\u0259rsliyin \\u0259sas m\\u0259qs\\u0259di t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 qeyri-formal t\\u0259hsilin m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif metodlar\\u0131n\\u0131 detall\\u0131 \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 \\u00e7atd\\u0131rmaqd\\u0131r.&nbsp;<br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>The video lesson discusses the concept and methods of non-formal education. Students are given general information about education, and then certain concepts are explained with examples. The main purpose of the course is to provide students with detailed information about the different methods of non-formal education.&nbsp;<\\/div>\"}', '[{\"text\":\"Thsil\"},{\"text\":\"Qeyri-formal\"}]', '2022-05-17 00:46:04', '2022-05-19 00:07:10'),
(60, '{\"en\":\"In the age of smartphones, the fact that marketing efforts are available on mobile devices is a well-known result. This course offers access to mobile marketing by looking at strategies to reach your target audience through many channels, including websites, email, social media, and mobile apps. Focusing on key concepts, definitions, and dimensions, the course explores ways specialists can take advantage of the unique advantages of mobile devices to ensure cost-effective customer performance.\",\"az\":\"Smartfonlar \\u0259srind\\u0259 marketinq s\\u0259yl\\u0259rinin mobil cihazda \\u0259l\\u00e7atan olmas\\u0131 ham\\u0131ya \\u0259vv\\u0259lc\\u0259d\\u0259n m\\u0259lum olan bir n\\u0259tic\\u0259dir. Bu kurs vebsaytlar, e-po\\u00e7t, sosial media v\\u0259 mobil proqramlar daxil olmaqla bir \\u00e7ox kanallar vasit\\u0259sil\\u0259 h\\u0259d\\u0259f auditoriyaya \\u00e7atmaq \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn strategiyalara baxaraq, mobil marketinq\\u0259 giri\\u015f t\\u0259klif edir. \\u018fsas anlay\\u0131\\u015flara, t\\u0259rifl\\u0259r\\u0259 v\\u0259 \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcl\\u0259r\\u0259 diqq\\u0259t yetirm\\u0259kl\\u0259, kurs marketoloqlar\\u0131n s\\u0259rf\\u0259li m\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u0259ri f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259tini t\\u0259min etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn mobil cihazlar\\u0131n unikal \\u00fcst\\u00fcnl\\u00fckl\\u0259rind\\u0259n istifad\\u0259yollar\\u0131n\\u0131 ara\\u015fd\\u0131r\\u0131r.\"}', 'Azrbaycan', '50', 7, 2, 39, 14, '{\"en\":\"Mobile Marketing\",\"az\":\"Mobil Marketinq\"}', 'D5OEiPN4at9ieC4v8HNtwanezGIVRVzu7W7JOLnt.png', '{\"az\":\"<div>Smartfonlar \\u0259srind\\u0259 marketinq s\\u0259yl\\u0259rinin mobil cihazda \\u0259l\\u00e7atan olmas\\u0131 ham\\u0131ya \\u0259vv\\u0259lc\\u0259d\\u0259n m\\u0259lum olan bir n\\u0259tic\\u0259dir. Bu kurs vebsaytlar, e-po\\u00e7t, sosial media v\\u0259 mobil proqramlar daxil olmaqla bir \\u00e7ox kanallar vasit\\u0259sil\\u0259 h\\u0259d\\u0259f auditoriyaya \\u00e7atmaq \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn strategiyalara baxaraq, mobil marketinq\\u0259 giri\\u015f t\\u0259klif edir. \\u018fsas anlay\\u0131\\u015flara, t\\u0259rifl\\u0259r\\u0259 v\\u0259 \\u00f6l\\u00e7\\u00fcl\\u0259r\\u0259 diqq\\u0259t yetirm\\u0259kl\\u0259, kurs marketoloqlar\\u0131n s\\u0259rf\\u0259li m\\u00fc\\u015ft\\u0259ri f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259tini t\\u0259min etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn mobil cihazlar\\u0131n unikal \\u00fcst\\u00fcnl\\u00fckl\\u0259rind\\u0259n istifad\\u0259yollar\\u0131n\\u0131 ara\\u015fd\\u0131r\\u0131r.<\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>In the age of smartphones, the fact that marketing efforts are available on mobile devices is a well-known result. This course offers access to mobile marketing by looking at strategies to reach your target audience through many channels, including websites, email, social media, and mobile apps. Focusing on key concepts, definitions, and dimensions, the course explores ways specialists can take advantage of the unique advantages of mobile devices to ensure cost-effective customer performance.<\\/div>\"}', '[{\"text\":\"Mobile\"},{\"text\":\"Marketing\"},{\"text\":\"google\"},{\"text\":\"ads\"}]', '2022-05-17 02:14:02', '2022-05-17 02:14:02'),
(61, '{\"en\":\"The course will teach students the importance of effective written and oral communication in a business environment. It also offers strategies that will allow them to communicate their ideas and values in a clear, convincing and memorable way. In this way, students will develop the skills to prepare effective business documents and present attractive presentations in a variety of business contexts. At the end of the course, students will be able to act as communicators who are ready to accept the communicative challenges inherent in today\'s dynamic business environment.\",\"az\":\"Kurs t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 i\\u015fg\\u00fczar m\\u00fchitd\\u0259 effektiv yaz\\u0131l\\u0131 v\\u0259 \\u015fifahi \\u00fcnsiyy\\u0259tin vacibliyini \\u00f6yr\\u0259d\\u0259c\\u0259k. H\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, onlara \\u00f6z fikirl\\u0259rini v\\u0259 d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259rini ayd\\u0131n, inand\\u0131r\\u0131c\\u0131 v\\u0259 yaddaqalan \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 \\u00e7atd\\u0131rma\\u011fa imkan ver\\u0259c\\u0259k strategiyalar t\\u0259klif edir. Bel\\u0259likl\\u0259, t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r effektiv biznes s\\u0259n\\u0259dl\\u0259ri haz\\u0131rlamaq v\\u0259 m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif biznes kontekstl\\u0259rind\\u0259 c\\u0259lbedici t\\u0259qdimatlar t\\u0259qdim etm\\u0259k bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n\\u0131 inki\\u015faf etdir\\u0259c\\u0259kl\\u0259r. Kursun sonunda t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r bug\\u00fcnk\\u00fc dinamik biznes m\\u00fchitin\\u0259 xas olan kommunikativ probleml\\u0259ri q\\u0259bul etm\\u0259y\\u0259 haz\\u0131r olan kommunikatorlar kimi f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259 bil\\u0259c\\u0259kl\\u0259r.\"}', 'Azrbaycan', '45', 4, 3, 40, 9, '{\"en\":\"Business Communication Management\",\"az\":\"\\u0130\\u015fg\\u00fczar kommunikasiyalar\\u0131n idar\\u0259 edilm\\u0259si\"}', 'a0xiez0MwwjGKasPw4hED3q36BiGXhdn3wZe7Nvc.png', '{\"en\":\"<div>The course will teach students the importance of effective written and oral communication in a business environment. It also offers strategies that will allow them to communicate their ideas and values in a clear, convincing and memorable way. In this way, students will develop the skills to prepare effective business documents and present attractive presentations in a variety of business contexts. At the end of the course, students will be able to act as communicators who are ready to accept the communicative challenges inherent in today\'s dynamic business environment.<\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Kurs t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 i\\u015fg\\u00fczar m\\u00fchitd\\u0259 effektiv yaz\\u0131l\\u0131 v\\u0259 \\u015fifahi \\u00fcnsiyy\\u0259tin vacibliyini \\u00f6yr\\u0259d\\u0259c\\u0259k. H\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, onlara \\u00f6z fikirl\\u0259rini v\\u0259 d\\u0259y\\u0259rl\\u0259rini ayd\\u0131n, inand\\u0131r\\u0131c\\u0131 v\\u0259 yaddaqalan \\u015f\\u0259kild\\u0259 \\u00e7atd\\u0131rma\\u011fa imkan ver\\u0259c\\u0259k strategiyalar t\\u0259klif edir. Bel\\u0259likl\\u0259, t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r effektiv biznes s\\u0259n\\u0259dl\\u0259ri haz\\u0131rlamaq v\\u0259 m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif biznes kontekstl\\u0259rind\\u0259 c\\u0259lbedici t\\u0259qdimatlar t\\u0259qdim etm\\u0259k bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131n\\u0131 inki\\u015faf etdir\\u0259c\\u0259kl\\u0259r. Kursun sonunda t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r bug\\u00fcnk\\u00fc dinamik biznes m\\u00fchitin\\u0259 xas olan kommunikativ probleml\\u0259ri q\\u0259bul etm\\u0259y\\u0259 haz\\u0131r olan kommunikatorlar kimi f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259r\\u0259 bil\\u0259c\\u0259kl\\u0259r.<\\/div>\"}', '[{\"text\":\"Communication\"},{\"text\":\"business\"}]', '2022-05-20 00:38:10', '2022-05-20 00:38:10'),
(62, '{\"en\":\"Project managers play a key role in managing, planning, and implementing critical projects to help organizations succeed. In this course, you will discover basic project management terminology and gain a deeper understanding of the roles and responsibilities of a project manager. The course also introduces students to the fundamental project management concepts and behavioral skills needed to successfully implement, lead and implement projects in commercial and non-profit organizations. Successful project managers skillfully manage their resources, schedules, risks, and coverage to achieve the desired results.\",\"az\":\"Layih\\u0259 menecerl\\u0259ri t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131n\\u0131n u\\u011fur qazanmas\\u0131na k\\u00f6m\\u0259k etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn kritik layih\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 r\\u0259hb\\u0259rlik etm\\u0259k, planla\\u015fd\\u0131rmaq v\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irm\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\u0259sas rol oynay\\u0131rlar. Bu kursda siz \\u0259sas layih\\u0259 idar\\u0259etm\\u0259 terminologiyas\\u0131n\\u0131 k\\u0259\\u015ff ed\\u0259c\\u0259k v\\u0259 layih\\u0259 menecerinin rolu v\\u0259 m\\u0259suliyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rini daha d\\u0259rind\\u0259n d\\u0259rk ed\\u0259c\\u0259ksiniz. H\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, kurs t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 kommersiya v\\u0259 qeyri-kommersiya t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131nda layih\\u0259l\\u0259ri u\\u011furla h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irm\\u0259k, onlara r\\u0259hb\\u0259rlik etm\\u0259k v\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn laz\\u0131m olan fundamental layih\\u0259 idar\\u0259etm\\u0259 konsepsiyalar\\u0131 v\\u0259 davran\\u0131\\u015f bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131 il\\u0259 tan\\u0131\\u015f edir. U\\u011furlu layih\\u0259 menecerl\\u0259ri ist\\u0259nil\\u0259n n\\u0259tic\\u0259ni \\u0259ld\\u0259 etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u00f6z resurslar\\u0131n\\u0131, c\\u0259dv\\u0259ll\\u0259rini, riskl\\u0259rini v\\u0259 \\u0259hat\\u0259 dair\\u0259sini m\\u0259har\\u0259tl\\u0259 idar\\u0259 edirl\\u0259r.\"}', 'English', '50', 7, 2, 30, 13, '{\"en\":\"Introduction to Project Management\",\"az\":\"Layih\\u0259l\\u0259rin idar\\u0259 olunmas\\u0131na giri\\u015f\"}', 'RQSiJbkHvWjt7NnRmrl4hUyCOaR7vDZforGFyjW2.png', '{\"en\":\"<div>Project managers play a key role in managing, planning, and implementing critical projects to help organizations succeed. In this course, you will discover basic project management terminology and gain a deeper understanding of the roles and responsibilities of a project manager. The course also introduces students to the fundamental project management concepts and behavioral skills needed to successfully implement, lead and implement projects in commercial and non-profit organizations. Successful project managers skillfully manage their resources, schedules, risks, and coverage to achieve the desired results.<br><br><\\/div>\",\"az\":\"<div>Layih\\u0259 menecerl\\u0259ri t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131n\\u0131n u\\u011fur qazanmas\\u0131na k\\u00f6m\\u0259k etm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn kritik layih\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 r\\u0259hb\\u0259rlik etm\\u0259k, planla\\u015fd\\u0131rmaq v\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irm\\u0259kd\\u0259 \\u0259sas rol oynay\\u0131rlar. Bu kursda siz \\u0259sas layih\\u0259 idar\\u0259etm\\u0259 terminologiyas\\u0131n\\u0131 k\\u0259\\u015ff ed\\u0259c\\u0259k v\\u0259 layih\\u0259 menecerinin rolu v\\u0259 m\\u0259suliyy\\u0259tl\\u0259rini daha d\\u0259rind\\u0259n d\\u0259rk ed\\u0259c\\u0259ksiniz. H\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, kurs t\\u0259l\\u0259b\\u0259l\\u0259r\\u0259 kommersiya v\\u0259 qeyri-kommersiya t\\u0259\\u015fkilatlar\\u0131nda layih\\u0259l\\u0259ri u\\u011furla h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irm\\u0259k, onlara r\\u0259hb\\u0259rlik etm\\u0259k v\\u0259 h\\u0259yata ke\\u00e7irm\\u0259k \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn laz\\u0131m olan fundamental layih\\u0259 idar\\u0259etm\\u0259 konsepsiyalar\\u0131 v\\u0259 davran\\u0131\\u015f bacar\\u0131qlar\\u0131 i