(6, 6, 10, '{\"en\":\"On 1 June the Launch Ceremony of Digiuth Online Platform was held at ADA University\",\"az\":\"\\u201cDigiuth\\u201d onlayn t\\u0259lim platformas\\u0131n\\u0131n a\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131\\u015f m\\u0259rasimi ba\\u015f tutub\"}', '9YO0VGDAT8rtkUskosboXjPdwY881XLtAa4DWEQ8.jpg', '<p>On June 1, 2022, the Launch Ceremony of Digiuth Online Learning platform was held at ADA University by the Erasmus Student Network - Azerbaijan public union. Chairman of the union Ali Tagiyev opened the event with an introductory speech and stressed the growing role of digital learning, innovations, and importance of digital non-formal education in development of the youth sector. Mihaly Gruber, Diplomat for Culture and Education at Hungarian Embassy in Baku, informed the participants about the mission of the International Visegrad Foundation and highligthed the importance of the opportunities created by the foundation in strengthening cooperation between Azerbaijan and the Visegrad group of countries. Ordukhan Gahramanzade and Heydar Rzayev, members of the management team of the Digiuth project, noted that the platform will bring significant innovation in the field of youth work by giving a detailed report on the project. Participants were informed about the future mission and goals of the platform and and interested parties were nvited to cooperate in the future as well. The launch ceremony was moderated by the National President of ESN Azerbaijan Ramiyya Shahgeldiyeva.</p><p>The Digiuth project is co-financed by the Governments of Czechia, Hungary, Poland, and Slovakia through Visegrad Grants from International Visegrad Fund. The mission of the fund is to advance ideas for sustainable regional cooperation in Central Europe.</p><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00023.jpeg\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00049-qrtyra.jpeg\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00055.jpeg\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00020.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00018-uaiqko.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00057-mg8m0m.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00077-8ywsdy.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00072-auac4t.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00021-umdzcu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\">', '<p style=\"text-align: justify\">1 iyun 2022-ci il tarixind Erasmus Tlb bksi  Azrbaycan ictimai birliyi trfindn ADA Universitetind Beynlxalq Vieqrad Fondu trfindn maliyyln Digiuth onlayn tlim platformasnn al mrasimi ba tutub. Birliyin sdri li Tayev tdbiri aq elan etdikdn sonra rqmsal yrnmnin, innovasiyalarn gnclr sektorunda v qeyri-formal thsilin inkiafnda artan rolundan sz ab. Digiuth layihsinin sas hdfinin&nbsp; lkmizd hr bir gnc n rqmsal yrnmni latan etmkdn ibart olduu qeyd edn li Tayev layihy gstrdiyi dsty gr layihnin trfdalarna v Beynlxalq Vieqrad Fonduna z tkkrn bildirib. Daha sonra x edn Macarstann Azrbaycandak sfirliyinin mdniyyt v thsil zr diplomat Mihaly Gruber itiraklara Beynlxalq Vieqrad Fondu haqqnda trafl mlumat verib v fondun yaratd imkanlarn Azrbaycan v Vieqrad qrupundan olan lklr arasnda mkdaln gclndirilmsind rolunun hmiyytini vurulayb. Daha sonra is Digiuth layihsinin idaretm qrupunun zvlri olan Orduxan Qhrmanzad v Heydr Rzayev platformann gnclrl i sahsin mhim bir yenilik gtircyini qeyd edib, layih haqqnda hesabat verib, platformann glck missiyas, hdflri barsind itiraklar mlumatlandrb v maraql trflri mkdala dvt ediblr.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">Szgedn al mrasimi birliyin milli prezidenti Ramiyy ahgldiyevann moderatorluunda ba tutub. Tdbird dvlt qurumlarnn, Vieqrad qrupundan olan lklrin sfirliklrinin v gnclr tkilatlarnn nmayndlri itirak ediblr. Mrasimin rsmi hisssindn sonra ay fasilsi tkil olunub v Macarstann lkmizdki sfirliyinin dstyi il azrbaycanl fotoqraflarn Vieqrad qrupundan olan lklrd kdiklri fotolar srgilnib.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\">Xatrladaq ki, Erasmus Tlb bksinin Azrbaycan nmayndliyi&nbsp; 2016-ci ild tbbs qrupu olaraq yaradlb, 2019-cu ild is rsmi qeydiyyata alnb. Birliyin sas faliyyt sahsi gnclrin Erasmus+ v digr proqramlar vasitsi il xaricd thsil almasna v tcrb qazanmasna dstk olmaq, Erasmus+ proqramnn mzunlar arasnda laq yaratmaq, beynlxalq knlllk proqramlarn tviq etmk, inkluziv thsilin inkiafna thf vermk, cnbi tlblrin (gnclrin) lkmizd sosial v mdni&nbsp; inteqrasiyasna yardm etmkdn ibartdir.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00023.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00049-qrtyra.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00055.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00041.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00020.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p style=\"text-align: justify\"></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00018-uaiqko.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00057-mg8m0m.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00077-8ywsdy.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00072-auac4t.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\"><p></p><img src=\"http://digiuth.com/uploads/image00021-umdzcu.jpeg\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" tt-mode=\"file\" tt-link-url=\"\" tt-link-target=\"\" tt-link-mode=\"url\" class=\"\">', '[{\"text\":\"Digiuth\"},{\"text\":\"ESN Azerbaijan\"},{\"text\":\"Onlayn Tlim\"},{\"text\":\"Al mrasimi\"},{\"text\":\"Vieqrad\"}]', '2022-06-04 14:37:10', '2022-06-04 15:14:34');
