(21, 0, 0, '{\"en\":\"Laman Guliyeva\",\"az\":\"L\\u0259man Quliyeva\"}', '{\"en\":\"Trainer\",\"az\":\"T\\u0259lim\\u00e7i\"}', 'SAmfIodAA3Z6n1Ond06HlAG22EZBOwkrCInzt22I.jpg', '{\"az\":\"<div>&nbsp;X\\u0259z\\u0259r Universitetinin Psixologiya fak\\u00fclt\\u0259si m\\u0259zunudur. Universitet ill\\u0259rind\\u0259n bir \\u00e7ox t\\u0259lim v\\u0259 konfranslara t\\u0259\\u015fkilat\\u00e7\\u0131l\\u0131q etmi\\u015f, daha sonra psixoterapiya v\\u0259 psixoloji konsultasiyalar \\u00fczr\\u0259 ixtisasla\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. H\\u0259m\\u00e7inin, psixoloji v\\u0259 karyera testl\\u0259rinin v\\u0259 karyera planlamas\\u0131 m\\u00f6vzusunun daxil oldu\\u011fu u\\u011furlu ixtisas se\\u00e7imi m\\u0259qs\\u0259di il\\u0259 yarad\\u0131lm\\u0131\\u015f \\\"\\u0130\\u015f\\u0131q\\\" platformas\\u0131n\\u0131n komanda \\u00fczvl\\u0259rind\\u0259n biridir. O, universitetd\\u0259 karyera inki\\u015faf\\u0131 v\\u0259 planlamas\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 \\u00e7al\\u0131\\u015fm\\u0131\\u015f, insan resurslar\\u0131 \\u00fczr\\u0259 \\u201cGDG Professionals\\u201d, ABB Bank kimi m\\u00fcxt\\u0259lif \\u015firk\\u0259tl\\u0259rd\\u0259 bilik v\\u0259 t\\u0259cr\\u00fcb\\u0259l\\u0259r qazanm\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r. Hal-haz\\u0131rda insan resurslar\\u0131 departamentind\\u0259&nbsp; t\\u0259lim v\\u0259 inki\\u015faf sah\\u0259si \\u00fczr\\u0259 f\\u0259aliyy\\u0259t g\\u00f6st\\u0259rir. Onun \\u0259n b\\u00f6y\\u00fck mara\\u011f\\u0131 insanlar \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn \\u015firk\\u0259t daxilind\\u0259 inki\\u015faf\\u0131 d\\u0259st\\u0259kl\\u0259y\\u0259n m\\u00fchit, sa\\u011flam m\\u00fcnasib\\u0259tl\\u0259r v\\u0259 y\\u00fcks\\u0259k i\\u015f m\\u0259mnuniyy\\u0259ti formala\\u015fd\\u0131rmaqd\\u0131r. Karyeras\\u0131na yeni ba\\u015flatan g\\u0259ncl\\u0259r\\u0259 d\\u0259st\\u0259k olmaq \\u00fc\\u00e7\\u00fcn Digiuth proyekti \\u00e7\\u0259r\\u00e7iv\\u0259sind\\u0259 \\u201cU\\u011furlu karyeran\\u0131 nec\\u0259 qurmal\\u0131?\\u201d adl\\u0131 video d\\u0259rsli haz\\u0131rlam\\u0131\\u015fd\\u0131r.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\",\"en\":\"<div>Laman Guliyeva is a graduate of Khazar University\'s Faculty of Psychology. During her university years, she organized many trainings and conferences, and later specialized in psychotherapy and psychological counseling. She is one of the team members of the \\\"Light\\\" start-up, which includes psychological and career tests, career planning, and a successful career choice. She has worked at the university on career development and planning, gaining knowledge and experience in the Human Resources departments of various companies such as GDG Professionals, and ABB Bank. She currently works in the training and development division of the HR. Her greatest interest is to create a supportive work environment, healthy relationships and high job satisfaction for people within the company. She has prepared a video lesson called \\\"How to Build a Successful Career?\\\" as part of Digiuth project in order to support young people who are just starting their careers.<br><br><\\/div><div><br><br><\\/div>\"}', NULL, NULL, 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/laman-guliyeva/', '2022-04-08 01:25:29', '2022-04-17 03:52:10'),
